<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<!--<h4>First Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrīmatu sakavaruśa 1201 pa māthisaṁva
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tsarada bhādrapada suddha chaṭi sōmavāradaṁdu śrīma
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Panel.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nu mūlasaṁghada padu<unclear>ma</unclear>sēnabhaṭārakadēvara gu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ḍi kaḍakoḷada sāvaṁta siriyamagauḍana heṁḍati
<lb n="5"/>caṁdigauḍi sa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> vrittiyaṁ kayikoṁḍu sa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mādhiyiṁ muḍipi svarggaprāpteyāda niśidhdhi(ḥ)
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ya staṁbha(ḥ) maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrī śrī
<lb n="8"/>hiryya boppagauḍa cika<unclear>bo</unclear>ppagauḍa cikkagauḍa
<lb n="9"/>kalidēvaru bādhyaviri <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> haṁneraḍu hi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṭu samasta praje basadige koṭṭa yare mattaru 1 <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrī śrī 
</p>

